{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:completion:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"userId"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"completion:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" (^"},{"kind":"text","text":")("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError","text":"NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"error"},{"kind":"text","text":")) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"userId","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The custom user identifier (e.g., database ID, UUID, username)."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Block called when the operation completes.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure."}]}],"name":"completion"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Same as "},{"code":"setUserId:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" but provides callback when the server operation completes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Use this when you need to ensure the user ID is set before performing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dependent operations like merging user data or tracking critical events."}]},{"level":2,"text":"Example","type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle login with guaranteed user ID synchronization:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class LoginCoordinator {","","    func performLogin(credentials: Credentials,","                      completion: @escaping (Result<User, Error>) -> Void) {","","        APIClient.shared.login(credentials) { result in","            switch result {","            case .success(let user):","                \/\/ Set user ID with confirmation before proceeding","                Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.id) { error in","                    if let error = error {","                        Logger.warning(\"User ID sync failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                        \/\/ Continue anyway - local state is still valid","                    }","","                    \/\/ Now safe to track login event with correct user attribution","                    Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                        \"logged_in\": true,","                        \"last_login\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","                        \"login_method\": credentials.method.rawValue","                    ])","","                    \/\/ Set email if available","                    if let email = user.email {","                        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(email)","                    }","","                    completion(.success(user))","                }","","            case .failure(let error):","                completion(.failure(error))","            }","        }","    }","}"]}]}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"setUserId:completion:","roleHeading":"Type Method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setUserId:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUserId:completion:","symbolKind":"method"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Sets a custom user identifier with completion confirmation.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:completion:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"title":"PushwooshCore","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setUserId:completion:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:completion:","title":"setUserId:completion:","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setUserId:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:completion:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setUserId:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Sets a custom user identifier with completion confirmation.","type":"text"}],"kind"